<div type="letter">
<pb facs="1038142" n="1"/>
  <opener><lb/><salute>Viro <abbr>pl.</abbr> Reverendo et Celeberrimo
    <lb/><rs type="person" key="pers_DE-588-119112450">Jacobo Hermanno</rs> <abbr>S. P. D.</abbr> <rs type="person"><abbr>N.B.</abbr></rs></salute></opener>
  <p><lb/>Diutius <choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>quo Tibi et merito quidem videbor distulisse debitam Tibi <choice><orig><g ref="#agrav">à</g></orig><reg>a</reg></choice> me gra<pc type="hyphenation">=</pc><lb break="no"/>tiarum actionem tum pro voto quo cathedram Mathematicam mihi delatam
    <lb/>et <choice><orig><g ref="#agrav">à</g></orig><reg>a</reg></choice> me tribus abhinc mensibus occupatam gratulari voluisti, tum pro iis
    <lb/>qu<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> me hac ex occasione monere dignatus es. Sed debiti hujus, quo me
    <lb/><del/>citius liberare <add>m</add>aluissem, pe<add>r</add>solutionem hactenus impedivere
    <lb/>negotia et cur<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>, quibus post meum in hanc <rs type="place">urbem</rs> adventum fere oppres<pc type="hyphenation">=</pc><lb break="no"/>sus fui. Accessit<del/> ingens<del/> ex funesta
    <lb/>et inopinata morte <rs type="person">Parentis</rs> mei,<del/> sub initium <add>fere</add> inaugurationis
    <lb/>me<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice><del/> defuncti conceptus dolor, qui molestias novi vit<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>
    <lb/>generis non leviter auxit, et <choice><orig><g ref="#egrav">è</g></orig><reg>e</reg></choice> contrario requiem animi mihi su<choice><orig><g ref="#mm">m̄</g></orig><reg>mm</reg></choice>opere
    <lb/>necessariam vehementer <del/><add>i<choice><orig><g ref="#mm">m̄</g></orig><reg>mm</reg></choice>inuit</add>. Nunc autem <del/><add>paululum</add> mihi redditus
    <lb/>has ad Te depropero, ut de grato meo in Te animo Tibi constet, Teque
    <lb/><del/>simul rogitem, ut pro amicitia quam mihi indulges, me porro mo<pc type="hyphenation">=</pc><lb break="no"/>nere pergas circa ea, qu<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> <del/><choice><orig><g ref="#agrav">à</g></orig><reg>a</reg></choice> <add>me</add> in <del/><add>eodem quo tu olim</add> loco <add>nunc</add> constituto optime fieri
    <lb/>posse judicas. Gratum facies, si geni<add>um</add><del/> <rs type="person">Professorum</rs> nostrorum mihi
    <lb/>describes, et qu<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> ipsorum intuitu cavenda esse expertus es significabis. Ne<pc type="hyphenation">=</pc><lb break="no"/>mine fere familiariter utor nisi <abbr>D.</abbr> Marchione <rs type="person" key="pers_DE-588-11887733X">Poleni</rs>, <abbr>DD.<hi rend="sup">os</hi></abbr> <abbr>P.</abbr> <rs type="person" key="pers_DE-588-1055630597">Burgos</rs>, <rs type="person" key="pers_DE-588-1055630597">Vallisneri</rs>,
    <lb/><rs type="person" key="pers_DE-588-104265264">Morgagni</rs>, <rs type="person" key="pers_DE-588-12898497X">Lazarini</rs> no<choice><orig><g ref="#nn">n̄</g></orig><reg>nn</reg></choice>unquam sed raro<del/> adeo; reliqui mihi
    <lb/>fere sunt barbari aut ego illis. <rs type="person">Petrus</rs> famulus olim Tuus<del/>
    <pb facs="1038143" n="2"/>
    <lb/>et mihi nunc servit. Nequam iste <rs type="person">uxore</rs>, quam in Patria duxerat, deserta<!-- ToDo: kontrollieren, ob "desertam" korrekter ist. -->
    <lb/>sub idem fere tempus quo ego in hanc <rs type="place">urbem</rs> venerat. Suspicor<del/> eum brevi
    <lb/>ad <rs type="person">uxorem</rs> rediturum esse, interim tamen gratum mihi pr<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>stabis, si qu<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> de
    <lb/>fide ejus Tibi constant, et quonam stipendio illum mactare solitus fueris, mihi
    <lb/>nuntiare non dedignaberis. Vidi hic impudentissimi <rs type="person" key="pers_DE-588-1089923198">Verzagli<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice></rs> <rs type="biblio">libellum</rs>
    <lb/>famosum, et stupui hominis audaciam et nequitiam. Recte facies si be<pc type="hyphenation">=</pc><lb break="no"/>stiam hanc posthac suo more vivere sines, cum qua disputare et ego
    <lb/>indecens esse puto. Optarem tamen ut <choice><orig><g ref="#agrav">à</g></orig><reg>a</reg></choice> quodam sub ficto aut tecto no<pc type="hyphenation">=</pc><lb break="no"/>mine perstringere<choice><orig><g ref="#tur">&#xf199;</g></orig><reg>tur</reg></choice>, quod fortassis ab amico quodam tuo fieri poterit.
    <lb/>Risum mihi mo<unclear>v</unclear>it dum in solutione sua Problematis mei distinguit
    <lb/>inter distantiam finitam et infinitam <choice><orig><g ref="#agrav">à</g></orig><reg>a</reg></choice> centro. Verum est <abbr>D.</abbr> <rs type="person" key="pers_DE-588-1156361761">Checozzi</rs>
    <lb/><del/>solam dedisse syntheticam demonstrationem<del/> solutionis
    <lb/>su<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>, sed qu<add>u</add>m illa talis sit, ut synthesis ipsius in analysin conversa solis
    <lb/>Parabolis aut hyperbolis applicari possit, tamdiu suspicabor eum
    <lb/>in analysi sua supposuisse, Curvam fore aliquam ex genere para<pc type="hyphenation">=</pc><lb break="no"/>bolarum, donec aliquam analysin ab omni tali suppositione liberam
    <lb/>proferat. Plane non assequor, quod dicis, Problema hac, <hi rend="u">data scala vel
    <lb/>virium vel temporum invenire alteram</hi> generaliter loquendo solvi non
    <lb/>posse seu <hi rend="u">implicare</hi>. An ergo si curva virium sit <abbr>ex.</abbr> <abbr>gr.</abbr> hyperbola ad
    <lb/>axem relata, mobile his viribus sollicitatum recta descendere non
    <lb/>poterit? Si sensum tu<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> assertionis capio <del/><add>videris</add> affirmare, mobile
    <lb/>recta descendere non posse, nisi urgeatur in singulis punctis vi qu<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>
    <lb/>sit ut dignitas aliqua distanti<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> <choice><orig><g ref="#agrav">à</g></orig><reg>a</reg></choice> centro; hoc autem verum esse mihi vix
    <lb/>persuadebis. Igitur cum mobile aliis viribus sollicitatum etiam descendere
    <lb/>possit et quidem <choice><orig><g ref="#agrav">à</g></orig><reg>a</reg></choice> quiete ex diversis distantiis, tempora descensuum expri<pc type="hyphenation">=</pc><lb break="no"/>mi poterunt per rectas lineas constituentes ordinatas curv<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> cujusdam,
    <lb/>et cuilibet dat<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> scal<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> virium respondebit aliqua scala temporum et
    <lb/>vicissim, adeo ut non videam, quomodo dicere possis Problema esse <hi rend="u">im</hi><pc type="hyphenation">=</pc><lb break="no"/>
    <pb facs="1038144" n="3"/> 
    <lb/><hi rend="u">possibile et implicare</hi> <del/><add>quoties</add> scala <del/><add>data non sit una</add> ex genere parabolar<choice><orig><g ref="#um">ū</g></orig><reg>um</reg></choice>.
    <lb/>Ego vero mihi videor <del/>posse solvere generaliter illud Problema, et ex
    <lb/>illa solutione <choice><orig><g ref="#agrav">à</g></orig><reg>a</reg></choice> priori deducere <rs type="keyword">parabolam Cubicam</rs> satisfacientem Proble<pc type="hyphenation">=</pc><lb break="no"/>mati <choice><orig><g ref="#agrav">à</g></orig><reg>a</reg></choice> me <del/>Italis proposito.</p> <closer>Vale et me ama. <dateline><rs type="place" key="place_GEO-3171728">Patavii</rs><choice><orig>.</orig><reg>,</reg></choice> <date when="1717-03-24">24 <abbr>Mart.</abbr> 1717</date>.</dateline></closer>
  <pb facs="1038145" n="4" type="empty"/> 
